      ███████║██████╔╝██║   ██║   ██████╔╝███████║    ██████╔╝██║   ██║ ╚████╔╝
      ██╔══██║██╔══██╗██║   ██║   ██╔══██╗██╔══██║    ██╔══██╗██║   ██║  ╚██╔╝
      ██║  ██║██║  ██║██║   ██║   ██║  ██║██║  ██║    ██║  ██║╚██████╔╝   ██║
      ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝   ╚═╝   ╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝    ╚═╝  ╚═╝ ╚═════╝    ╚═╝

      Research Assistant / Doctoral Researcher,
      Chemical Process and Energy Engineering,
      London South Bank University, UK
